<p>Matthew is the Creative Director at <a href="http://www.zaarly.com/">Zaarly</a>, the mobile, real-time place to ask for anything and get it nearby. He speaks internationally on design, writes for <a href="http://www.netmagazine.com/">.net Magazine</a>, and believes in love. Matthew lives in Greenville, South Carolina where he founded <a href="http://coworkgreenville.com/">CoWork Greenville</a>.</p><p>You can follow his tweets <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/whale">@whale</a>.</p>